  5 Thus Mischn
 Aboth, v
 21, "at forty years of age a man comes to intelligence
" This verse refers, it is said by the Sonnites, to Abu Bekr, afterwards Chalif, who embraced Islam in his 40th year
 But this interpretation was probably invented after his accession to power
