 suffer loss
  7 The Prophet Houd
  8 That is, Sandhills; at Taief, to which Muhammad had retired in consequence of the opposition, etc
, of the Meccans
 Verses 20-31 are probably misplaced, as they interrupt the connection between 19 and 32, but appear to belong to the same period as the rest of the Sura
  9 Thus Ullm
